<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أز ف:</span> <span class="c2">(أَزِفَ)</span> الرَّحِيلُ دَنَا وَبَابُهُ طَرِبَ.<span class="c5"> وَمِنْهُ قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{أَزِفَتِ الْآزِفَةُ}</span> <span class="c4">[النجم: ٥٧]</span> يَعْنِي الْقِيَامَةَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>